- 마이크로바이옴 + 면역 + 대사 (cross-microbiome)
- 환경 stress + 면역 + 대사 (cross-environmental)
- 노화 + 면역 + 대사 (cross-aging immunosenescence)
- COVID-19 + immunometabolism + long COVID (cross-chronic_fatigue)
- HSCT + GvHD metabolic (cross-transplant + bone_marrow_failure)
- T cell exhaustion + 대사 (cross-cancer immune)
- inflammasome + NLRP3 + 만성 염증 (cross-cardiology Lodoco 2023)
