## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **canakinumab CANTOS 2017** = first 항-염증 CV prevention (IL-1β mAb). atherosclerosis 가 LDL 만이 아닌 만성 염증 driven 임을 임상 input. cross-cardiology + preventive paradigm shift.
2. **colchicine Lodoco 2023** = first FDA CV prevention drug (anti-inflammatory). LoDoCo2 RCT. IL-1β + inflammasome + tubulin myeloid metabolic. cheap generic 의 paradigm 재발견.
3. **rilonacept Arcalyst 2023 recurrent pericarditis** = IL-1 trap. CAPS 2008 → 재발 심낭염 2023 expansion. cross-cardiology immunometabolic.
4. **relatlimab Opdualag 2022** = first FDA LAG-3 inhibitor (with nivolumab). melanoma 1L. metabolic-checkpoint paradigm. quantum-VQE PPI scaffold fit.
5. **telaglenastat CB-839 fail 2021** = glutaminase Phase 3 RCC (CANTATA) + NSCLC (KEAPSAKE) negative. tumor monotherapy 한계 → IO synergy paradigm 으로 재정렬. hxq-immet-glutam-001 의 raison.
6. **vibostolimab + tiragolumab TIGIT fail 2024** = Roche SKYSCRAPER-01 NSCLC negative. TIGIT 단독 Phase 3 limit. checkpoint additivity 가설 재고.
7. **IDO1 epacadostat fail 2018** = KEYNOTE-252 melanoma negative. tryptophan metabolism + IO 가 임상 fail. mechanism 자체 보다는 patient selection 한계.
8. **semaglutide SELECT 2023** = GLP-1 첫 CV prevention in obesity (without diabetes). 면역 + 대사 modulation 임상. cross-obesity + cardiology + immunometabolic.
9. **adenosine A2A + 4-1BB + OX40 + TIM-3 Phase 2-3** = next-wave checkpoint expansion. metabolic-immune crosstalk 의 임상 plurality.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, immunometabolism 임상 의미 한정. cross-paradigm orthogonal entry.

